│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ Let's re-examine the problem and my failed solution.                                                                                                                                     │
│ The core issue is that the SLP vectorizer is trying to combine two `icmp slt` instructions:                                                                                              │
│ 1.  `icmp slt (sext i16 to i32), (zext i16 to i32)`                                                                                                                                      │
│ 2.  `icmp slt (sext i16 to i32), (zext i16 to i32)`                                                                                                                                      │
