│ #     return TreeEntry::Vectorize;                                                                                                                                                       │
│ #   }                                                                                                                                                                                    │
│ # My incorrect patch was inserted at 7674. The file now has my old code there.                                                                                                           │
│ # I need to replace my old code with the new code.                                                                                                                                       │
